      "file_path": "datarouter-node/src/main/java/org/onap/dmaap/datarouter/node/DeliveryTask.java",
      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 49,
      "message": "I agree thats its a much cleaner way to write the code, however I'm unable to use getClass() in a static context, like in the case of the logger. \n\nHowever I used DeliveryTask.class to replace the string path. is this acceptable? its not generic, but at least we don't have problems with restructuring the package, and its possible to use ide tools to copy/paste relatively easily.\n\nAlso, I presume these changes should be done across all of dr?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4439,
        "name": "Emmett  Cox",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "emmett.cox@ericsson.com",
        "username": "EmmettCox"
      },
      "updated": "2019-01-31 16:28:31.000000000",
